summary: Three jungle style ambient sound files.
descriptionHtml:
There are two sound files in the archive.

1) New Sound File Looped. (Daytime)
Has running water sounds with jungle birds and insects and toad noises.

2) New Sound File Looped Aternative. (Night-time)
Has low wind sounds with night-time insect sounds.  There is a single monkey sound along with a splash of water sound (perhaps he fell off his tree.)  Also there is a hawk sound with other jungle bird chatter.

3) New Sound File Looped Scary.
Adds a new loop that has some scary ambient sounds.
author: Jimmytrouser
